Romney: Obama's 'Dishonesty' Will Cost Him

One year after his losing bid for the presidency, Mitt Romney gave an exclusive interview on Meet the Press, slamming Obamacare. Also on Sunday Talk: Lindsey Graham's Benghazi play and Chris Christie.
